<h1 style="color: #e8e8e8;">New Message on Order</h1>

<p style="color: #b7b7b7;">Hello {{userDisplayName}},</p>

<p style="color: #b7b7b7;">{{message.author}}
  sent a message on order "{{order.title}}":</p>

<div
  style="background-color: rgba(45, 55, 72, 0.5); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgb(45, 55, 72); border-left: 4px solid #7a7efe;"
>
  <p
    style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #b7b7b7;"
  >{{message.content}}</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="button">View Order & Reply</a>
</p>